Package org.hibernate.query.sqm.mutation.internal

Class MultiTableSqmMutationConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.query.sqm.spi.BaseSemanticQueryWalker
      • org.hibernate.query.sqm.sql.BaseSqmToSqlAstConverter<Statement>
        • org.hibernate.query.sqm.mutation.internal.MultiTableSqmMutationConverter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SemanticQueryWalker<Object>, JdbcParameterBySqmParameterAccess, SqmToSqlAstConverter, SqmTranslator<Statement>, FromClauseAccess, SqlAstCreationState, DomainResultCreationState, JdbcTypeDescriptorIndicators
    public class MultiTableSqmMutationConverter
extends BaseSqmToSqlAstConverter<Statement>
    Specialized BaseSqmToSqlAstConverter implementation used during conversion of an SQM mutation query tree representing into the various SQL AST trees needed to perform that operation.
    See Also:
    visitSetClause(SqmSetClause, Consumer, SqmParameterResolutionConsumer), visitWhereClause(SqmWhereClause, Consumer, SqmParameterResolutionConsumer), visitSelectClause(SqmSelectClause, QuerySpec, Consumer, SqmParameterResolutionConsumer)
